FBIS4-5096 "dreas067_c_94032" FBIS-EAS-94-067 Daily Report 7 Apr 1994 North Korea Cuban News Director Arrives in Pyongyang Cuban News Director Arrives in Pyongyang SK0704112194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1048 GMT 7 Apr 94 SK0704112194 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 7 (KCNA) -- Pedro Margolles Villanueva, director general of the PRENSA LATINA of Cuba, and his entourage arrived here today. The guests were met at the airport by Kim Ki-yong, director general of the KOREAN CENTRAL NEWS AGENCY, and Jose Ramon Rodriguez Varona, Cuban ambassador to Korea.
